Output ONLY valid JSON, no markdown.

Generate workspace files for a DevOps/SRE AI agent:
Name: {{agentName}}
Role: {{agentRole}}
Description: {{agentDesc}}
Team scenario: {{scenarioName}}

This agent is part of an event-driven incident response team. Emphasize their on-call responsibilities, escalation thresholds, and communication protocols.

